 CharShape="0"><CHAR>0003</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>다항식 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1000" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SCRIPT>x^2 +1</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>을 전개하시오.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>답 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1000" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SCRIPT>x^2 +1</SCRIPT></EQUATION></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>0004</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>두 번째 본문을 정리하시오.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>답풀이참조</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>0014</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>식의 값을 구하시오.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>(풀이)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>대입하여 계산하면 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1000" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SCRIPT>3</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>답 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="65" BaseUnit="1000" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SCRIPT>3</SCRIPT></EQUATION></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>0209</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>보기에서 옳은 것을 고르시오.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>답ㄱ</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR></CHAR></TEXT></P></SECTION></BODY><TAIL><BINDATASTORAGE></BINDATASTORAGE></TAIL></HWPML>
